data.description: Reduced...Cash or Conventional Buyers! Short Sale! Lovely Bungalow in the Evergreen historic distict. Home will be sold "AS IS" min. away from downtown Memphis. Renovated 2 yrs ago includes beautiful hardwood floors, new roof, fixtures, updated bathrooms, stainless steel appliances, large porch & deck great space. 3 large bedrooms, 2 full baths, large fenced backyard and basement. ALL appliances will stay and are as-is. A must see...CALL AGENT for a private tour.
